# DoorDash imports use the Chrome extension (see /extension in the repo).

# --- Supabase (required for login + cloud sync) ---
# Project URL and PUBLIC anon key from Supabase Dashboard → Settings → API.
# The anon key is safe to ship in the browser bundle — Row-Level Security
# enforces access. NEVER put the service_role key here.
# VITE_SUPABASE_URL=https://YOUR-PROJECT.supabase.co
# VITE_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY=eyJ...

# --- AI Enhancement ---
# The Anthropic key now lives SERVER-SIDE in the `ai-enhance` Supabase Edge
# Function — it is no longer in the browser bundle. Set it as a function secret:
#   supabase secrets set ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
# Then deploy:  supabase functions deploy ai-enhance
